HE CLEARS THROAT

17:32.920 --> 17:34.760
DRINK POURS

17:37.560 --> 17:39.640
Can I be honest with you?

17:39.640 --> 17:42.480
I keep forgetting I'm pregnant.

17:42.480 --> 17:45.760
- You forget? 
- Yeah, yeah...

17:45.760 --> 17:47.600
