17:58.120 --> 18:01.480
and grabbing me when I got home, so, I had enough.

18:01.480 --> 18:02.840
Got rid of him.

18:02.840 --> 18:04.680
Good.

18:06.120 --> 18:08.640
Well, better without.

18:08.640 --> 18:09.960
You?

18:09.960 --> 18:11.320
Yeah, we're together.

18:12.400 --> 18:13.440
Yeah...

18:13.440 --> 18:15.080
He doesn't live here though, does he?

18:15.080 --> 18:17.000
You can tell, it's spotless.

18:17.000 --> 18:18.680
Yeah, well...

18:19.880 --> 18:21.520
Long story.

18:24.560 --> 18:25.800
Go on.

18:28.040 --> 18:30.920
'People say that the perfect story is that you meet this one person

18:30.920 --> 18:33.320
'and fall completely in love, and then from that moment,'

18:33.320 --> 18:35.040
